{"tid":2244122,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS更新與國安關係","createTime":"2020-10-15T09:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T12:33:53.000Z","uid":247112,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1c244e6cb68b9700822970bf30e21e2daf1d8f8a","tid":2244122,"uid":247112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T09:06:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://blog.zh-hant.playstation.com/2020/10/14/20201014-ps5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.zh-hant.playstation.com%2F2020%2F10%2F14%2F20201014-ps5%2F&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzp1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=637d8bfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.zh-hant.playstation.com/2020/10/14/20201014-ps5/</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;在此更新之後，用戶將會看到「派對安全」相關通知，告知派對內的語音聊天可能會被錄音。為調解而設計的語音聊天錄音功能將在PS5上市時一併推出，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"teal\">可讓用戶在PS5上錄下其語音聊天並提交供調解審核</span></span>。目前用戶會在PS4上看到的彈出視窗是告知當你跟PS5用戶（上市後）進行聊天，他們可以提交那些在PS5主機上的錄音給SIE使用。  &quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以後咩friend搭friend、打機group、唔熟既, 都唔好開PARTY傾計打機, 一個唔該條友小粉紅/藍底/奶共狗，錄低D對話, 你講一聲&quot;香港國&quot;，分分鐘已經仆街。<br />\n<br />\n自己睇路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f5560805346ef6a27bb07fca88a5beb6a9e237","tid":2244122,"uid":343268,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T09:17:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ea2ac5317e4e7e43055c4027d8f217becf02799","tid":2244122,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T09:47:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87347bdcad0d7eb4d11ef8b9abfaa5d3bd7c98d9","tid":2244122,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T09:47:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6947c309e83e1fa8bb1e747ccdb80935e30de78","tid":2244122,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T09:48:17.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"a6e283c2bebe0170cc0947f45c9383c34871d731","tid":2244122,"uid":169071,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1c244e6cb68b9700822970bf30e21e2daf1